data.description: This home is located in a secluded cul-de-sac on a large fully landscaped 9,600sqft lot with mature trees for added privacy, wood cedar fencing, automatic sprinkler system front and back. Large 2 car detached heated garage! Patio area, private deck from dining area that overlooks the back yard! 1 car attached garage leading to the great room for ease of access! Inside you'll find a great room with living room, dining area and galley kitchen with 2 pantries and lots of counter space!,Additionally Main level offers main bath, 2 bedrooms and master suite with 3/4 bath, lower level includes family room with entertainment area with fireplace, master suite with custom bath, launder/utility room and lots of storage!
